description.displayText: Vivian was absolutely phenomenal! She came to our hotel and watched our 9 month old while we attended a wedding. I highly recommend Vivian !

description.displayText:
Viviane R has been babysitting for my children for over a year. She's one of the most reliable and dependable people I have ever worked with. She is always punctual and has never canceled on us last minute. In case of emergencies, Viviane is genuinely eager to help out.

My children enjoy her company and feel safe and cared for by her. I often see them engaged very thoughtful and animated conversations. She is very articulate, friendly, and responsible. It has been a pleasure to get to know Viviane and work with her this past year.

description.displayText:
Vivian was last minute help for me very early morning around 6:45 AM (considering that situation, an angel God sent to help me) when my other babysitter cancelled on me just 45 minutes before job start time. Fortunately Vivian responded back to my job post very early in the morning and was at my place in next 15 minutes - I hired a cab for her to be at my place quickly but she did all she could to start in next 5 minutes to be at my place considering the emergency situation I had to take care of, not eating her breakfast, leaving everything else behind. I appreciate her understanding and willingness so much to help me be with the unexpected bad situation before extremely important appointment in next one hour. Cannot thank her enough for understanding my panic. She was very pleasant and willing to help with whatever I needed help with. My son loved spending time with her. 

I recommend her very strongly and will hire her again!!!
